data.description: The time is now to make this gorgeous farmhouse your new home! It has everything you have been looking for and more! The fantasy begins when you drive through the picturesque landscape of the Canton Golf Club and view this beautiful white farmhouse sitting on five acres, high on a hill, overlooking the green. When you pull into the driveway, and wind up to the house, you can't help but notice the stately beams and wide front porch welcoming you home. Once inside, the open floorpan, and chef's kitchen, complete with a hidden walk-in pantry, is a perfect place to entertain; especially on those upcoming fall nights with the huge back porch and fire pit. If serenity is more your style, the master bath has everything you need... a large soaking tub and an oversized glass shower with custom tile. With 5 bedrooms and even a storm shelter and whole house generator, what more could anyone ask for?
